he failure at the Asian Games was a huge blow to me,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 981, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The failure\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 928}, {\"ngram\": \"the Asian Games\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 947}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge blow\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 963}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was very frustrated for the rest of the year.\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 1030, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1017}, {\"ngram\": \"the year\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1029}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whenever I thought about it during practice, negative emotions would haunt me.\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1109, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"practice\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1074}, {\"ngram\": \"negative emotions\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1093}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was difficult for me to adjust my mindset.\\\"\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1156, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my mindset\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1154}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Chinese national team began their winter training camp after the Asian Games and invited a new coach, Huang Zuping, to help Luo improve his riding.\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1309, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1162, \"end\": 1183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.99846283066882, \"rank\": 0.0010699478557765145, \"text\": \"Chinese national team\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1286, \"end\": 1289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luo_people\", \"score\": 0.9580241020274003, \"rank\": 0.031864512320044856, \"text\": \"Luo\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luo_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luo_people\"}], \"noun_ph